    <briefdescription>
<para>this object stores a difference between two vectors with 3D coordinates </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>if the vectors are similar then this object is small, if the vectors are very distinct then this object will be even larger than one vector itself Generated from class <computeroutput><ref refid="classMR_1_1VertCoordsDiff" kindref="compound">MR.VertCoordsDiff</ref></computeroutput>. This is the non-const half of the class. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
